snippet.textDisplay: This was not expected of Coke Studio. Juth bolte sharam nahi aati. This song is a folk song you idiot. I didnt know it before but as soon as I read your claim that kailash wrote ot on his father's death, my suspicion arose. How can anyone be so spiritually mature to write such a celebrative song on his own father's death? Only a person who is detached from worldly matters can see his own father as nothing but a soul. And  no one can be such a saint. I googled it and saw my doubts were right. Its a folk song. Matlab agar limit mein juth bolte to pakde nahi jaate... jyada honshiyaari marne gaye usme hi pakde gaye.
